items.title:
[ ] Avoid HTML comments in view templates as these are viewable to clients. Use server-side comments instead:<p>```
  # bad - HTML comments will be visible to users who "View Source":
  <!-- This will be sent to clients --></p><p># ok - ERB comments are removed by the server, and so not viewable to clients:
  &lt;%# This will <em>not</em> be sent to clients %&gt;
  &lt;%#= link_to "Admin Site", "https://admin.example.org/login" %&gt;
  ```</p>
